  "projection_rules": [
    "Statutes and government-wide regulations usually bind at federal-us scope unless narrower scope is curated.",
    "USDA and USFS directives usually bind at administrative scope and may also bind at region scope when the issuing surface is region-specific.",
    "Forest plans bind at forest_unit_scope and must also carry governed forest-unit identity.",
